pageContext.claim: “Getting great reviews, finally, for how well we are handling the pandemic, especially our strong production of desperately needed ventilators, the building of field hospitals & beds, and soon, the great things we are doing on testing. People are really working well together!”
pageContext.analysis: The administration did not get “great reviews.” It bumbled several steps in the response to covid-19, which led the virus to spread undetected for a number of weeks.
